Privacy Policy
This privacy policy sets out how Ranida Games uses and protects any information that you provide when using applications or services provided by Ranida Games. Ranida Games is committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected. Should we ask you to provide certain information by which you can be identified when using the application or service, then you can be assured that it will only be used in accordance with this privacy statement. Ranida Games may change this policy from time to time by updating this page. This policy is effective from Jan 1st, 2016.
​
What we collect
We may collect the following information:
Contact information (email address)
Device and device OS information
Usage statistics
​
What we do with the information we gather
We require this information to understand your needs and provide you with a better service, and in particular for the following reasons:
​
Providing technical support via email
We may use the anonymous usage information to improve our products and services
​
Security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. In order to prevent unauthorised access or disclosure we use industry standard practices and cryptographic methods to safeguard and secure the information we collect online.
​
Third-party content and services
Our applications and services may contain third-party functionality and content that is not under our control. This functionality and content is not governed by this privacy statement. Ranida Games assumes no responsibility whatsoever for the content provided by third parties, or functionality provided by third-party SDKs. These third-party elements include:
​
In-game functionality that may require a separate login (Such as ad networks or video sharing communities)
Links to external websites
Any user-generated content such as game levels or image files
​
Controlling your personal information
We will not sell, distribute or lease your personal information to third parties unless we have your permission or are required by law to do so. If you believe that any information we are holding on you is incorrect or incomplete, please contact us at
info@ranidagames.com
. We will promptly correct any information found to be incorrect.
​